B.Ej=s(["Para alacaklar\u0131n\u0131n tahsilinin g\xfcvence alt\u0131na al\u0131nmas\u0131","Uyu\u015fmazl\u0131k konusu (\xe7eki\u015fmeli) \u015fey veya hak hakk\u0131nda koruma sa\u011flanmas\u0131","Bor\xe7lunun hapsen tazyiki","Kesinle\u015fmi\u015f bir karar\u0131n icras\u0131"],t.s)
