B.Do=s(["\u0130kisi de yaln\u0131zca para alacaklar\u0131 i\xe7indir.","\u0130htiyati tedbir \xe7eki\u015fmeli \u015fey/hak i\xe7in (HMK), ihtiyati haciz para alaca\u011f\u0131 i\xe7in (\u0130\u0130K) \xf6ng\xf6r\xfclm\xfc\u015ft\xfcr.","\u0130htiyati haciz dava a\xe7\u0131lmadan hi\xe7 istenemez.","\u0130htiyati tedbir yaln\u0131zca icra dairesinden istenir."],t.s)
