B.Je=new A.b3("kanun_04",B.bZ,'Malvarl\u0131\u011f\u0131na ili\u015fkin davalarda istinaf "kesinlik s\u0131n\u0131r\u0131" ne anlama gelir?',B.DH,0,"HMK m. 341: Miktar veya de\u011feri belirli bir tutar\u0131 ge\xe7meyen malvarl\u0131\u011f\u0131 davalar\u0131na ili\u015fkin kararlar kesindir (istinaf edilemez). Bu s\u0131n\u0131r her y\u0131l yeniden de\u011ferleme oran\u0131nda artar; g\xfcncel tutar\u0131 teyit et.")
B.DK=s(["Kesinlik s\u0131n\u0131r\u0131n\u0131n alt\u0131nda kal\u0131rsa istinafa g\xf6t\xfcr\xfclemez.","Miktar\u0131na bak\u0131lmaks\u0131z\u0131n istinaf yolu a\xe7\u0131kt\u0131r.","Manevi tazminat kararlar\u0131 hi\xe7bir \u015fekilde istinaf edilemez.","Yaln\u0131zca davac\u0131 istinafa ba\u015fvurabilir."],t.s)
